---
import { Code, Layers, MapPin, Rocket } from '@lucide/astro'
---

<div class='space-y-8 rounded border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow'>
    {/* Intro */}
    <div class='space-y-3'>
        <h1 class='flex items-center gap-2 text-2xl font-bold'>Hey 👋</h1>
        <p class='leading-relaxed text-slate-700'>
            I'm <span class='font-semibold'>Ajvad Laseen</span>, a full-stack
            developer currently working in{' '}
            <span class='font-medium text-blue-600'>Dubai 🇦🇪</span>.
        </p>
        <p class='leading-relaxed text-slate-700'>
            For the past <strong>4+ years</strong>, I've been living in the
            world of Full Stack Development where the main tools in my arsenal
            were:
        </p>
        <ul class='mt-3 space-y-2 text-slate-800'>
            <li class='flex items-center gap-2'>
                <Code class='h-5 w-5 text-sky-600' />{' '}
                <strong>React</strong>
            </li>
            <li class='flex items-center gap-2'>
                <Code class='h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600' />{' '}
                <strong>TypeScript</strong>
            </li>
            <li class='flex items-center gap-2'>
                <Code class='h-5 w-5 text-green-600' />{' '}
                <strong>Node.js</strong>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    {/* Industries */}
    <div class='flex flex-row space-y-3'>
        <div class='flex items-start gap-2 leading-relaxed text-slate-700'>
            <Layers class='mt-1 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-purple-600' />
            <p>
                I've had the pleasure to work across a bunch of industries, from{
                    ' '
                }
                <span class='font-bold'>Construction</span> to{' '}
                <span class='font-bold'>HR</span>,{' '}
                <span class='font-bold'>Real Estate</span>, and even{' '}
                <span class='font-bold'>Hospitality</span>. Every project taught
                me something new and each of them came with its own set of wild
                challenges.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    {/* Motivation */}
    <div class='space-y-3'>
        <p class='flex items-start gap-2 leading-relaxed text-slate-700'>
            <Rocket class='mt-1 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-red-600' />
            At the end of the day what really makes me happy is building software
            that actually makes people's lives easier and my learning deeper.
        </p>
    </div>

    {/* Conclusion */}
    <div class='space-y-3'>
        <p class='flex items-start gap-2 leading-relaxed text-slate-700'>
            <MapPin class='mt-1 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-blue-600' />
            Feel free to explore and check out my work, skills, and projects. And
            if you want to reach out to me for anything related to the above or just
            a quick chat, you may use any of the communication channels mentioned.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
